        "karlstad-anneberg-problem-9": {
          "description": {
            "text": "Starts on obvious holds. Establish yourself using the feature up and right in the roof, then launch for the lip. From there, a somewhat exposed and very high, but relatively easy, top-out awaits. Bring plenty of pads and preferably more than one spotter, as you rarely know where you will land. An excellent problem strongly reminiscent of Helikoptere at Bas Cuvier, for those who have tried or climbed it. Top 5 in Karlstad! The top-out was unbrushed in July 2012. Give it a good scrub with a wire brush before committing!",
            "method": "llm",
